Sentencas: Strontium cobalt oxide (SrCoO3-delta) nanoparticles were successfully synthesized using; composite mediated hydrothermal (CMHM), without water and surfactants (WOWS) sol-gel and co-precipitation methods.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: The probable electrical conduction mechanism of synthesized strontium cobaltite was investigated via complex impedance analysis.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Characterization techniques were employed to study the dependence of structure, homogeneity, physical parameters and electrical properties on synthesis procedures.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: After heat treatment, X-Ray Diffraction (XRD) confirmed the formation of phase pure SrCoO(3-delta)powders synthesized with CMHM, WOWS sol-gel and co-precipitation methods.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Fourier Transform Infrared Spectroscopy (FTIR) spectra indicated the presence of fingerprint region of perovskite (ABO(3-delta)) structure.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Raman spectroscopy revealed the internal motion of oxygen inside the CoO(6)octahedra of SrCoO(3-delta)perovskite structure.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: A Raman phonon mode under 600 cm(-1)position was identified which is commonly observed for such perovskite oxide.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Scanning Electron Microscopy (SEM) images showed uniformly diffused, microporous and agglomerated sphere like morphology.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Differential Thermal Analysis (DTA) and Thermogravimetry (TGA) verified formation of intermediate metal carbonates that decomposed to final product.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Complex impedance spectroscopic plots (Nyquist plots) against frequency (20 Hz-3 MHz) discovered single semi-circular arcs in the low frequency region.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: These arcs showed that, grain boundary contribution is dominated over grain contribution to the total electrical conduction behavior.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Modulus analysis disclosed non-Debye type conductivity relaxation in hydrothermally synthesized samples.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: The AC conductivity graphs followed Jonscher's power law and hopping model.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes

Sentencas: Hydrothermally synthesized samples exhibited minimum impedances and maximum AC conductivity, which makes them excellent candidate for cathode material in intermediate temperature range solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) applications.
Titulo: Conductivity relaxations and phase purity in strontium cobalt oxides prepared by numerous chemical routes
